# Place your photos here

## Folder structure

```
public/images/
├── hero.jpg              ← Hero section main photo
├── closing.jpg           ← Closing section background
├── timeline/
│   ├── met.jpg
│   ├── first-kiss.jpg
│   └── official.jpg
├── gallery/
│   ├── 01.jpg
│   ├── 02.jpg
│   └── ...
└── events/
    ├── graduation/
    │   ├── 01.jpg
    │   ├── 02.jpg
    │   └── 03.jpg
    └── anniversary/
        └── 01.jpg
```

Supported formats: `.jpg`, `.jpeg`, `.png`, `.webp`

Recommended: compress photos before adding (under 500KB each for fast loading).
